{"tid":1452832,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"引入老解二步曲, 緊急!","createTime":"2019-08-12T02:29:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T05:12:22.000Z","uid":251584,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f174a4d875a6308c094858e249d56a504ce4face","tid":1452832,"uid":251584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:29:21.000Z","msg":"777同狗係絶對可以<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">合法地短時間</span></strong>内加入<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>大陸公安或老解</strong></span>入嚟香港做狗, 由612開始, 已經大把時間比佢deploy. <strong><em><span style=\"color: red;\">方法?</span></em></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係利用每日150單程證同Cap 232 24條</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<em>24. 臨時警務人員<br />\n(1)處長可不以書面聘約而僱用任何人臨時出任警務人員。<br />\n(2)臨時警務人員須當作為按月服務，而此等聘用須視為由每個相繼月份的第一天開始，至該月份的最後一天可終止，但即使該聘用有上述條款，該警務人員就有關薪金、津貼、酬金及退休金的服務條件而言，須與相等職級的輔警人員相同，而在其如此服務期間，他具有及可行使該職級的一切權力及特權，並受該職級的一切紀律條文所規限。  (由1959年第2號附表2修訂；由1969年第29號第2條修訂；由1997年第362號法律公告修訂；由1999年第58號第3條修訂)<br />\n(3)臨時警務人員，可獲給予1個月的書面通知而隨時予以解僱，或可給予處長1個月的書面通知，或事先經處長同意，向庫務署繳付1個月的薪金以代替通知而辭職。  (由1953年第13號第5條修訂)<br />\n(由1950年第29號第8條代替)</em><br />\n<br />\n<strong>假設7.1後開始, 到今日8.12 係43日, 好有可能已經有<span style=\"color: red;\">6450個公安/老解</span>做緊狗狗.</strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">而家需要咁多位手足推到記者, 議員, IMMI手足都知道.</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>IMMI手足</strong>: IMMI group內廣傳, 相關同事留意有無異狀? 如最近150個單程證都係青壯年男子?<br />\n<strong>記者同議員</strong>: 要你地問777,狗狗, 有無使用Cap 232 24條? 提供相關資料! 問埋IMMI單程證既情況!<br />\n<strong>巴絲</strong>:幫手指正,俾料同廣傳!<br />\n<br />\n推!"},{"pid":"a9349f1c16fcef74482dc7617f2661628be8549e","tid":1452832,"uid":251584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:29:37.000Z","msg":"自推!"},{"pid":"fcccf63d8d0ff49bf4b0db391b04d4b827a948be","tid":1452832,"uid":251584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:32:19.000Z","msg":"引入老解二步曲, 緊急!"},{"pid":"58f4f5a7da18fe515c92bc0b68635e00616b44ab","tid":1452832,"uid":46314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:36:57.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"01748d0e4d4d5ca174efffea3cdd2efe0bdfd93d","tid":1452832,"uid":251584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:37:39.000Z","msg":"幫手推！"},{"pid":"e9a01c7422676f6b1c5f99ff27cda624a43efa09","tid":1452832,"uid":99516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:38:25.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ce595eeab5476f8a7bfdf641e20af9e20091ca49","tid":1452832,"uid":135536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:45:20.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"dea58e0465ea1d7f09293969fc79abcc2e4b0a16","tid":1452832,"uid":251584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:54:12.000Z","msg":"再推！"},{"pid":"2fc4466ccf9ffea22a5e0dc3ab41f44dc8dae1bd","tid":1452832,"uid":251584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:54:22.000Z","msg":"老解呀！"},{"pid":"e3376d91a50e206cae25a7311eaa925a2a1c47ff","tid":1452832,"uid":251584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:54:33.000Z","msg":"屌！人呢？"},{"pid":"2ce7406f3811eaacf79e230a27bb82f4a396d4f1","tid":1452832,"uid":251584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:17:43.000Z","msg":"幫手推！"},{"pid":"173de0349f41d7d6c648149e5d8d9df193e766a9","tid":1452832,"uid":251584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:01:51.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"b2282de1997410d4a90f04d35177f53decf41b4f","tid":1452832,"uid":251584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T06:34:47.000Z","msg":"再推！"},{"pid":"a3d4371f36c10217616464e1b361fc7fa9c90ed7","tid":1452832,"uid":251584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:21:18.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"caf60eddb2dd86fe62cc6280c3d66a645c3c4270","tid":14